title: KCRW.com - Top Tunes April 2008
description:
Collected from KCRW.com as their free daily download.  MP3 format, 128KBPS, 44KHz.  Files are uniformly named with embedded album covers and M3U playlist.

If you like what you hear, I strongly urge you to join KCRW as a member or donate to the station (KCRW.com or at 89.9 FM in the LA area).  Enjoy!
